OL,3,CMPs open inquiry into special
OL,4,Ceducational needs and disabilities
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FThe Education Committee launched an
OL,8,Finquiry on Friday to try and find
OL,9,Fsolutions to the crisis in SEND
OL,10,Fprovision and to ensure the system's
OL,11,Flong-term sustainability.
OL,13,FIt comes after concerns have been
OL,14,Fraised that the system in England is
OL,15,Ffailing to support young people and
OL,16,Ftheir families.
