OL,3,CMPs open inquiry into special
OL,4,Ceducational needs and disabilities
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FExclusive research from ITV News in
OL,8,FJuly found that more than half of
OL,9,Fchildren (58%) with special
OL,10,Feducational needs had to take time out
OL,11,Fof school because their needs were not
OL,12,Fbeing met.
OL,14,FIn October, the National Audit Office
OL,15,F(NAO) said the system is "financially
OL,16,Funsustainable" as councils warned they
OL,17,Fcould go bankrupt "overnight" due to
OL,18,Fthe surging cost of SEND provisions.
