OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FLast week, the Institute for Fiscal
OL,8,FStudies (IFS) said local authorities'
OL,9,Fhigh-needs deficits could reach more
OL,10,Fthan #8 billion by 2027.
OL,12,FEarlier this month the government
OL,13,Fassigned #740 million of funding to
OL,14,Fcreate more specialist places in
OL,15,Fmainstream schools.
OL,17,FThe committee will also examine the
OL,18,Feffectiveness of education, health and
OL,19,Fcare plans (ECHP), a legal document
OL,20,Fthat sets out the additional support
OL,21,Frequired to reach those needs.
