OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FCommittee chair, Helen Hayes said: "In
OL,8,Frecent years, report after report has
OL,9,Fdocumented the failures of the Send
OL,10,Fsystem to deliver the support children
OL,11,Fand their families need.
OL,13,F"Despite the best efforts of
OL,14,Fprofessionals in schools and local
OL,15,Fauthorities, across the country,
OL,16,Fchildren are being let down.
OL,26,@oD@dOUuD@AOU
