OL,3,CMPs open inquiry into special
OL,4,Ceducational needs and disabilities
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,F"As a Committee, we now want to move
OL,8,Fbeyond simply pointing out the
OL,9,Fproblems and focus on finding
OL,10,Fsolutions that are realistic and
OL,11,Fpractical for the Government to
OL,12,Fimplement.
OL,14,F"This crisis has many symptoms that
OL,15,Fbleed into the rest of the education
OL,16,Fsystem: from attrition in the teaching
OL,17,Fworkforce to soaring levels of pupil
OL,18,Fabsence.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
