OL,3,CMPs open inquiry into special
OL,4,Ceducational needs and disabilities
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,F"There are also symptoms which blight
OL,8,Flocal councils' budgets ` ever
OL,9,Fincreasing spending on transporting
OL,10,Fpupils to settings far from where they
OL,11,Flive, and the chaos of money being
OL,12,Fpoured into tribunals that parents are
OL,13,Fexpected to win.
OL,15,F"It's widely accepted that many more
OL,16,Fcouncils could face effective
OL,17,Fbankruptcy if change doesn't come
OL,18,Fsoon."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@FO]
