OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,F"This situation leaves children
OL,8,Fwithout the timely support that they
OL,9,Frequire, families feeling desperate
OL,10,Fand frustrated, and schools under
OL,11,Fimmense pressure.
OL,13,F"These are not new problems and yet
OL,14,Fmeaningful action to address them has
OL,15,Fso far remained elusive."
